OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,7,F(CMA) said Monday they found evidence
OL,8,Feight housebuilders may be sharing
OL,9,Fcommercially sensitive information
OL,10,Fwith their competitors, which could be
OL,11,Finfluencing the build-out of sites and
OL,12,Fthe prices of new homes.
OL,14,FThe CMA said that while it "does not
OL,15,Fconsider such sharing of information
OL,16,Fto be one of the main factors in the
OL,17,Fpersistent under-delivery of homes",
OL,18,Fit is "concerned that it may weaken
OL,19,Fcompetition in the market."
