OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FUnder the Competition Act 1998, the
OL,7,FCMA said it is looking into the UK's
OL,8,Feight largest housebuilders: Barratt,
OL,9,FBellway, Berkeley, Bloor Homes,
OL,10,FPersimmon, Redrow, Taylor Wimpey, and
OL,11,FVistry.
OL,13,FThe report also raised concerns about
OL,14,Festate management charges, which it
OL,15,Fsaid may come with inadequate
OL,16,Fprotections for consumers.
OL,18,FHomebuyers may be poorly informed when
OL,19,Fit comes to important details about
OL,20,Fsuch arrangements and their long-term
OL,21,Fimplications, the watchdog said.
