OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FIt found a growing trend by developers
OL,7,Fto build estates with privately-
OL,8,Fmanaged public amenities ` with 80% of
OL,9,Fnew homes sold by the 11 biggest
OL,10,Fbuilders in 2021 to 2022 subject to
OL,11,Festate management charges.
OL,13,FBills can be high, with a large
OL,14,Fproportion relating to administration
OL,15,For management fees, and future bills
OL,16,Fmay be unpredictable and potentially
OL,17,Fvery high as amenities degrade over
OL,18,Ftime, the CMA said.
