OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FThe charges can relate to the
OL,7,Fmaintenance of public spaces like
OL,8,Fgreens or children's play areas.
OL,10,FBut homeowners across the country have
OL,11,Fcomplained of the high cost of these
OL,12,Fmaintenance charges compared to the
OL,13,Fwork that needs doing if it even gets
OL,14,Fdone at all.
OL,16,FEstate management companies have huge
OL,17,Fsway in the market and have little
OL,18,Freason to deliver services at a
OL,19,Freasonable price or to an acceptable
OL,20,Flevel of quality, the CMA added.
