OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FWhile the average charge was #350, one-
OL,7,Foff, unplanned charges for significant
OL,8,Frepair work can cost thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds and cause considerable stress
OL,10,Fto homeowners, the CMA said.
OL,12,FThe report also noted the extreme
OL,13,Fcomplexity of switching estate
OL,14,Fmanagement providers and the lack of
OL,15,Finformation homeowners are given
OL,16,Fupfront.
OL,18,FAnalysis also suggests that a growing
OL,19,Fnumber of homeowners are reporting a
OL,20,Fhigher number of snagging issues, the
OL,21,Fwatchdog said.
