OL,3,CHousebuilders working together to keep
OL,4,Cprices high, watchdog claims
OL,6,FThe CMA's consumer research indicated
OL,7,Fthat a substantial minority had also
OL,8,Fexperienced particularly serious
OL,9,Fproblems with their new homes, such as
OL,10,Fcollapsing staircases and ceilings.
OL,12,FThe watchdog said it wants to see a
OL,13,Fhousebuilding market that delivers
OL,14,Fconsistently better outcomes on new-
OL,15,Fbuild quality, with consumers having
OL,16,Fan effective route to redress, as well
OL,17,Fas reduced detriment to consumers
OL,18,Farising from the private management of
OL,19,Fpublic amenities on new-build estates.
